comments: I\'ve had 3 classes with him and I think he\'s great. He is soft spoken so you can\'t sit in the back but he gives you paper copies of all his powerpoint notes from each class.(awesome-you don\'t have to take notes)Usually requires 1 paper(5-6pg). Multiple choice tests which he hand feeds you the answers to before hand. Easy class, but you\'ll learn alo
John D is a good teacher. Helpful and will answer any question u have.

He speaks soft so sit in front. He reveiws the chapters slowly, lots of discussion sometimes too much class stories especially when reveiwing for test. Very helpful reveiwing tests (when staying on task), covers answers in details and tests are multiple choice, at least in all the classes I have had with him. Nice man!!
